<item>
  <title>Gem in Eyes — an introduction</title>
  <link>https://derekwakefield.com/apps/2026-05-09-gem-in-eyes-intro.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>A small light in a deep room. A cube of stone with five lit corners and one quiet pocket at the center. You hum, and the room hums back. Five gods — <strong>Lik</strong>, <strong>Ton</strong>, <strong>Ren</strong>, <strong>Nif</strong>, <strong>Eye</strong> — keep the corners lit.</p>
<p>This piece is a self-contained HTML file. Download it and open it locally in any browser.</p>
